content: HI, I joined as a texter, almost a month ago, have friends who want to phone bank.  What is the best way to have them join so they can use the Dawn to Dusk dialer?

Either you can train them if you're comfortable doing that, or they can sign up for a traditional Zoom phone bank to get the training then jump in here. 
Are they already on Discord?
No, they aren't... I guess that is what I am asking... how do they get here...
OH! You just send them an invite: https://discord.gg/kQQn7Bsb
I can explain the dialer and the process to them (I have hopped over there when waiting for new campaigns)
Thanks for bringing friends into the fold! We love volunteer squads!
Thanks for doing all of this. We are going to win!!!
